"Narrated 'Abdullah:\"A Jew came to the Prophet (ﷺ) and said: 'O Muhammad! Allah will seize the heavens upon a finger, the mountains upon a finger, the earths upon a finger, and the rest of creation upon a finger. Then He says: 'I am the King.'\" He said: 'So the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) laughed until his molars were visible. He said: \"They made not a just estimate of Allah such as is due to Him (39:)"